'''Anarchy''' ''([[noun]])''

:# Absence of a [[government]].
:# Absence of [[hierarchy]], [[power]] and [[authority]].
:# A general condition characterised by the ability of each [[actor]] to have a say in [[outcome]]s [[proportionate]] to the degree they are [[affected]] by those outcomes.
:# without rules or laws (syn: [[anomie]], [[anomy]])
:# self-government ([http://www.lewrockwell.com/orig/neill1.html])

